<div class="homepage-container">
  <div class="heading">
     <h1>"Revive the Glamour of the Past" </h1>
     <p>"<span>Experience the timeless elegance and sophistication of a bygone era.</span> Rent a piece of history today and embark on a journey through time behind the wheel of a meticulously preserved vintage automobile. Whether it's for a special occasion, a memorable road trip, or simply to indulge in the nostalgia of classic motoring, our collection of vintage cars awaits you. Step back in time and make memories that will last a lifetime with our vintage car rental service."</p>
      <%= link_to "See our cars", cars_path, class: "link" %>
  </div>
  <div class="photo-container">
    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
      </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="app/assets/images/blue_cabrio.png" alt="First slide">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="app/assets/images/vintage_porsche.png" alt="Second slide">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="app/assets/images/orange_car_rome.png" alt="Third slide">
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div>


  </div>
</div>
